"Through a <literal>GitRepo</literal> resources - <xref linkend=\"k8s-upgrade-"
"suc-plan-deployment-git-repo\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースを使用する - <xref linkend=\"k8s-upgrade-"
"suc-plan-deployment-git-repo\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1958
