#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2148
msgid ""
"Navigate to the <literal>Longhorn CRD</literal> Chart fleet located under "
"<literal>fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn-crd</literal>:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn-crd</literal>にある"
"<literal>Longhorn CRD</literal>チャートフリートに移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
