msgstr ""
"<literal>01-fix-growfs.sh</literal>スクリプトは、デプロイメント時にOSルート"
"パーティションをサイズ変更するために必要です。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2862
msgid ""
"<literal>02-airgap.sh</literal> script is required to copy the images to the "
"right place during the image creation process for air-gapped environments."
